from qsample.examples import ghz3, flagstab
from qsample.sim.stabilizer import StabilizerSimulator as CHP
from qsample.noise import E1, E2
from qsample.callbacks import *

e = E2
# e = E1

sample_range = np.logspace(-3,0,5)

err_probs = {
    "q1": sample_range ,
    "q2": sample_range,
    # "init": 0,
    # "meas": 0,
    # "idle": 0
}
pmax = {
    "q2" : 0.1,
    "q1": 0.1,
    # "init": 0,
    # "meas": 0,
    # "idle": 0
}

sam = SubsetSampler(flagstab, CHP, pmax=pmax, err_probs=err_probs, err_model=e)
sam.run(100, callbacks=[PlotStats()])
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
sam.tree.draw()

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

p_L_low, ss_std_low, p_L_up, ss_std_up = sam.stats()
plt.loglog(sample_range,ss_std_low)
plt.loglog(sample_range,ss_std_up)
